-- Brookfield Asset Says It Supports Talks With Brookfield Homes on Carma
-- Bill Koenig
-- 2010-07-30T11:27:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-30/brookfield-asset-says-it-supports-talks-with-brookfield-homes-on-carma.html

          
          
             Brookfield Homes Corp. said it
intends to commence discussions with Brookfield Properties Corp.
regarding a possible merger that would result in the combination
of Brookfield Homes with Carma Developers.  
          
          


  


        